{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-001__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-001", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·001.1", "text_original": "文王在上，於昭于天。周雖舊邦，其命維新。\n有周不顯，帝命不時。文王陟降，在帝左右。", "text_normalized": "文王在上，於昭于天。周雖舊邦，其命維新。\n有周不顯，帝命不時。文王陟降，在帝左右。", "notes": "文王 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-001__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-001", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·001.2", "text_original": "亹亹文王，令聞不已。陳錫哉周，侯文王孫子。\n文王孫子，本支百世。凡周之士，不顯亦世。", "text_normalized": "亹亹文王，令聞不已。陳錫哉周，侯文王孫子。\n文王孫子，本支百世。凡周之士，不顯亦世。", "notes": "文王 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-001__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-001", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·001.3", "text_original": "世之不顯，厥猶翼翼。思皇多士，生此王國。\n王國克生，維周之楨。濟濟多士，文王以寧。", "text_normalized": "世之不顯，厥猶翼翼。思皇多士，生此王國。\n王國克生，維周之楨。濟濟多士，文王以寧。", "notes": "文王 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-001__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-001", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·001.4", "text_original": "穆穆文王，於緝熙敬止。假哉天命，有商孫子。\n商之孫子，其麗不億。上帝既命，侯于周服。", "text_normalized": "穆穆文王，於緝熙敬止。假哉天命，有商孫子。\n商之孫子，其麗不億。上帝既命，侯于周服。", "notes": "文王 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-001__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-001", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·001.5", "text_original": "侯服于周，天命靡常。殷士膚敏，祼將于京。\n厥作祼將，常服黼冔。王之藎臣，無念爾祖。", "text_normalized": "侯服于周，天命靡常。殷士膚敏，祼將于京。\n厥作祼將，常服黼冔。王之藎臣，無念爾祖。", "notes": "文王 Chinese stanza 5."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-001__006__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-001", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·001.6", "text_original": "無念爾祖，聿脩厥德。永言配命，自求多福。\n殷之未喪師，克配上帝。宜鑒于殷，駿命不易。", "text_normalized": "無念爾祖，聿脩厥德。永言配命，自求多福。\n殷之未喪師，克配上帝。宜鑒于殷，駿命不易。", "notes": "文王 Chinese stanza 6."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-001__007__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-001", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-001__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·001.7", "text_original": "命之不易，無遏爾躬。宣昭義問，有虞殷自天。\n上天之載，無聲無臭。儀刑文王，萬邦作孚。", "text_normalized": "命之不易，無遏爾躬。宣昭義問，有虞殷自天。\n上天之載，無聲無臭。儀刑文王，萬邦作孚。", "notes": "文王 Chinese stanza 7."}
